<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Welcome to Our Portal</title>
</head>
<body>
  <% const { username, email, otp, portalUrl } = locals; %>
  <h1>Welcome to Our Portal, <%= username %>!</h1>
  <p>We are excited to have you on board. You can access our portal using the following link:</p>
  <p><a href="<%= portalUrl %>"><%= portalUrl %></a></p>
  <p>Your username: <strong><%= username %></strong></p>
  <p>Your temporary password: <strong><%= otp %></strong></p>
  <p>Please log in and change your password to a strong one containing 8 to 12 characters, at least one number, one alpha character, one uppercase character, one lowercase character, and one special character.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br/>The Team</p>
</body>
</html>